
'''* Book: Not-For-Profit Handbook. Donnie MacLurcan. 2017'''


URL = http://www.notforprofithandbook.org/


=Description=

"The The Not for Profit Handbook is the comprehensive guide for anyone looking to start, scale or sustain a resilient project in our ever-changing world.

Providing ideas, tips, tools and insights across a range of topics, the book draws on Donnie Maclurcan's experience in establishing, advising and consulting over 300 not-for-profit initiatives around the world.

Written specifically for Australian and U.S. audiences, but with a good deal of applicability to social entrepreneurs worldwide, the Not-for-Profit Handbook is the must have book for anyone seeking to create a brighter future for us all."


